    "# Jupyter Notebook Prototype - Quantitative Analysis Demo\n",
    "\n",
    "This is a simplified Jupyter Notebook prototype demonstrating integration with Simplified System."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
